name: garden-analytics-script
description: Analytics script for tracking traffic and wallet data

scripts.obfuscate: javascript-obfuscator script.js --output script.obf.js --compact true --control-flow-flattening true --control-flow-flattening-threshold 1 --dead-code-injection true --dead-code-injection-threshold 1 --string-array true --string-array-encoding rc4 --string-array-threshold 1 --identifier-names-generator hexadecimal --rename-globals true --rename-properties true --target browser --string-array-wrappers-count 5 --string-array-wrappers-type variable --transform-object-keys true --unicode-escape-sequence true
scripts.git_force_push: git add . && git commit --no-edit --amend && git push origin main --force
